{"image_id": "SBAC_2006_page_32", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "Table of Contents", "bbox": [37.5, 90.8, 206.4, 119.6]}, {"text": "RESULTS OF OPERATIONS", "bbox": [37.5, 143.2, 319.9, 172.3]}, {"text": "Year Ended 2006 Compared to Year Ended 2005", "bbox": [37.5, 175.7, 483.7, 204.8]}, {"text": "Revenues:", "bbox": [37.5, 208.2, 139.4, 237.3]}, {"text": "Site leasing revenue increased due to the increased number of new tenant installations, the amount of lease amendments related to", "bbox": [85.5, 464.2, 1173.7, 491.8]}, {"text": "equipment added to our towers, revenue generated by the towers that we acquired in the AAT Acquisition, other towers acquired, and towers", "bbox": [37.5, 487.4, 1218.2, 515.1]}, {"text": "constructed during 2006. The AAT Acquisition contributed approximately $63.2 million of the increase in total revenues. As of December 31,", "bbox": [37.5, 510.4, 1229.4, 538.1]}, {"text": "2006, we had 13,602 tenants as compared to 8,278 tenants at December 31, 2005. Additionally, we have experienced on average, higher rents", "bbox": [37.5, 533.4, 1223.9, 561.1]}, {"text": "per tenant due to higher rents from new tenants, higher rents upon renewal by existing tenants and additional equipment added by existing", "bbox": [37.5, 556.7, 1193.9, 584.3]}, {"text": "tenants. Lastly, we added 2,249 towers to our portfolio in 2006 versus only adding 244 towers in 2005.", "bbox": [37.5, 579.7, 906.2, 607.3]}, {"text": "Site development consulting revenues increased as a result of a higher volume of work in 2006 versus 2005. Site development", "bbox": [85.5, 621.4, 1142.4, 649.1]}, {"text": "construction revenue decreased due to the roll-off of certain of our prior construction contracts from the larger wireless carriers and our efforts", "bbox": [37.5, 644.4, 1230.4, 672.1]}, {"text": "to focus on capturing the higher margin services work rather than volume.", "bbox": [37.5, 667.7, 665.9, 695.3]}, {"text": "Operating Expenses:", "bbox": [37.5, 718.7, 233.7, 747.8]}, {"text": "Site leasing cost of revenues increased primarily as a result of the growth in the number of towers owned by us, which was 5,551 at", "bbox": [85.5, 1074.4, 1186.4, 1102.1]}, {"text": "December 31, 2006 up from 3,304 at December 31, 2005. The AAT Acquisition contributed approximately $19.6 million to the increase in", "bbox": [37.5, 1097.4, 1202.7, 1125.1]}, {"text": "total site leasing cost of revenues. Site development consulting cost of revenues increased as a result of higher volume of work for the year", "bbox": [37.5, 1120.7, 1199.7, 1148.3]}, {"text": "ended December 31, 2006 versus the same period of 2005. Site development construction cost of revenue decreased due to the roll-off of", "bbox": [37.5, 1143.7, 1185.2, 1171.3]}, {"text": "certain of our prior construction contracts from the larger wireless carriers and our efforts to focus on capturing the higher margin services", "bbox": [37.5, 1166.7, 1195.7, 1194.3]}, {"text": "work rather than volume. That focus and changing market conditions for the year ended December 31, 2006 resulted in higher margin jobs in", "bbox": [37.5, 1189.7, 1220.7, 1217.3]}, {"text": "2006 versus 2005.", "bbox": [37.5, 1212.9, 200.2, 1240.6]}, {"text": "29", "bbox": [627.0, 1253.4, 652.9, 1281.1]}, {"text": "For the year ended December 31,", "bbox": [692.7, 254.6, 919.4, 276.0]}, {"text": "2006", "bbox": [598.7, 308.6, 633.9, 330.0]}, {"text": "Percentage", "bbox": [697.5, 291.1, 775.4, 312.5]}, {"text": "of Revenues", "bbox": [694.2, 308.6, 800.1, 330.4]}, {"text": "2005", "bbox": [856.5, 308.6, 891.6, 330.0]}, {"text": "Percentage", "bbox": [955.2, 291.1, 1033.1, 312.5]}, {"text": "of Revenues", "bbox": [952.0, 308.6, 1057.9, 330.4]}, {"text": "Percentage", "bbox": [1091.0, 273.6, 1168.9, 295.0]}, {"text": "Change", "bbox": [1102.2, 308.6, 1172.9, 330.4]}, {"text": "(in thousands except for percentages)", "bbox": [745.2, 327.6, 998.9, 349.0]}, {"text": "Site leasing", "bbox": [85.5, 343.7, 187.